summary: a job search website for hospitality jobs in the Netherlands. The website allows users to search for jobs by location, department, and contract type. The listed jobs include various positions at the Mövenpick Hotel Amsterdam City Centre, such as Banqueting Employee, Sales & Marketing Trainee, and Bartender. The website also provides information on top departments and popular job searches in the Netherlands. Users can create an account to save and apply for jobs later.
